{
  "stem": "25912.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I believe that he purchased some South American visas for us to leave as well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He had no intention of going to Romania.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He wanted to rejoin the Polish army, which we heard had been formed in France.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And all went reasonably well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He had to go to the Gestapo to-- to be interviewed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And despite the wonderful German bureaucracy, while he was at the Gestapo headquarters, they telephoned the Archives Department to check on him, and somehow missed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So he was given a passport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But, to get your visa-- exit visa, it had to be stamped by the governor of the occupied territory, who was stationed in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was General Frank.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And to get that required a bribe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There were specialists who used to take passports to be stamped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I remember that everything was already packed, my father's cases and our own cases.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I had my favorite Shirley Temple doll dressed in traveling clothes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The German customs had been to the flat to stamp the cases.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "When the specialist came back and said that things weren't quite right, and he was afraid of giving three passports in the same name to be stamped on one occasion.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So he decided that my father's and my brother's passport were the most important ones, but that he would get ours stamped the following week.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "My father was all for waiting for us to leave together, but Mother was so anxious, felt that, every day, they were in danger.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "She insisted that they should leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they left on the 6th of April.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Well, things did not work out the way it was planned.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Because, somehow, our passports didn't come until much later, by which time the German offensive on Holland and Belgium had started.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
